                  <span xml:lang="en"
                        target="#T04_AD_F.67_Naameh_Maslaxbefore4_a55"
                        xml:id="a60">There was war. It is true that people were besieged Dekwaneh, in the  Maslakh (area), (but) people were living.</span>
               </spanGrp>
            </div>
            <div xml:id="T04_AD_F.67_Naameh_Maslaxbefore4_a12">
               <u xml:lang="ar-acm-x-shawi-vicav"
                  who="corpus:LEB_NAA_2023_AD_F.67_Speaker1"
                  xml:id="T04_AD_F.67_Naameh_Maslaxbefore4_a12_u1"
                  end="#T30"
                  start="#T29">
                  <gap reason="unconsented"/>
               </u>
               <spanGrp type="Translation">
                  <span xml:lang="en"
                        target="#T04_AD_F.67_Naameh_Maslaxbefore4_a12"
                        xml:id="a41">People were living in every thing (sense).</span>
               </spanGrp>
            </div>
            <div xml:id="T04_AD_F.67_Naameh_Maslaxbefore4_a13">
               <u xml:lang="ar-acm-x-shawi-vicav"
                  who="corpus:LEB_NAA_2023_AD_F.67_Speaker1"
                  xml:id="T04_AD_F.67_Naameh_Maslaxbefore4_a13_u1"
                  end="#T31"
                  start="#T30">
                  <gap reason="unconsented"/>
               </u>
               <spanGrp type="Translation">
                  <span xml:lang="en"
                        target="#T04_AD_F.67_Naameh_Maslaxbefore4_a13"
                        xml:id="a42">I mean the rich and the poor wasn't feeling that there was a difference. the people were living better than those days.</span>
               </spanGrp>
            </div>
            <div xml:id="T04_AD_F.67_Naameh_Maslaxbefore4_a14">
               <u xml:lang="ar-acm-x-shawi-vicav"
                  who="corpus:LEB_NAA_2023_AD_F.67_Speaker1"
                  xml:id="T04_AD_F.67_Naameh_Maslaxbefore4_a14_u1"
                  end="#T32"
                  start="#T31">
                  <gap reason="unconsented"/>
               </u>
               <spanGrp type="Translation">
                  <span xml:lang="en"
                        target="#T04_AD_F.67_Naameh_Maslaxbefore4_a14"
                        xml:id="a43">You could go anywhere with one pound, or half a pound.</span>
               </spanGrp>
            </div>
            <div xml:id="T04_AD_F.67_Naameh_Maslaxbefore4_a56">
               <u xml:lang="ar-acm-x-shawi-vicav"
                  who="corpus:LEB_NAA_2023_AD_F.67_Speaker1"
                  xml:id="T04_AD_F.67_Naameh_Maslaxbefore4_a56_u1"
                  end="#T33"
                  start="#T32">
                  <gap reason="unconsented"/>
               </u>
               <spanGrp type="Translation">
                  <span xml:lang="en"
                        target="#T04_AD_F.67_Naameh_Maslaxbefore4_a56"
                        xml:id="a61">Now what?</span>
               </spanGrp>
            </div>
            <div xml:id="T04_AD_F.67_Naameh_Maslaxbefore4_a57">
               <u xml:lang="ar-acm-x-shawi-vicav"
                  who="corpus:LEB_NAA_2023_AD_F.67_Speaker1"
                  xml:id="T04_AD_F.67_Naameh_Maslaxbefore4_a57_u1"
                  end="#T35"
                  start="#T34">
                  <gap reason="unconsented"/>
               </u>
               <spanGrp type="Translation">
                  <span xml:lang="en"
                        target="#T04_AD_F.67_Naameh_Maslaxbefore4_a57"
                        xml:id="a62">Now if you want to go to Beirut, how much does it cost you?</span>
               </spanGrp>
            </div>
            <div xml:id="T04_AD_F.67_Naameh_Maslaxbefore4_a58">
               <u xml:lang="ar-acm-x-shawi-vicav"
                  who="corpus:LEB_NAA_2023_AD_F.67_Speaker1"
                  xml:id="T04_AD_F.67_Naameh_Maslaxbefore4_a58_u1"
                  end="#T37"
                  start="#T36">
                  <gap reason="unconsented"/>
               </u>
               <spanGrp type="Translation">
                  <span xml:lang="en"
                        target="#T04_AD_F.67_Naameh_Maslaxbefore4_a58"
                        xml:id="a63">I went down to Beirut, do you know how much we spent me and K? Six hundred thousand for the (taxi) trip.</span>
               </spanGrp>
            </div>
            <div xml:id="T04_AD_F.67_Naameh_Maslaxbefore4_a15">
               <u xml:lang="ar-acm-x-shawi-vicav"
                  who="corpus:LEB_NAA_2023_AD_F.67_Speaker1"
                  xml:id="T04_AD_F.67_Naameh_Maslaxbefore4_a15_u1"
                  end="#T38"
                  start="#T37">
                  <gap reason="unconsented"/>
               </u>
               <spanGrp type="Translation">
                  <span xml:lang="en"
                        target="#T04_AD_F.67_Naameh_Maslaxbefore4_a15"
                        xml:id="a44">People are now cutting down on many things.</span>
               </spanGrp>
            </div>
            <div xml:id="T04_AD_F.67_Naameh_Maslaxbefore4_a16">
               <u xml:lang="ar-acm-x-shawi-vicav"
                  who="corpus:LEB_NAA_2023_AD_F.67_Speaker1"
                  xml:id="T04_AD_F.67_Naameh_Maslaxbefore4_a16_u1"
                  end="#T39"
                  start="#T38">
                  <gap reason="unconsented"/>
               </u>
               <spanGrp type="Translation">
                  <span xml:lang="en"
                        target="#T04_AD_F.67_Naameh_Maslaxbefore4_a16"
                        xml:id="a45">and that who works in illegal matters, lives. That who... You and I, can we work in illegal/sinful matters? no, God is sufficient... May God suffice us with what is permissible and keep us away from what is forbidden.</span>
               </spanGrp>
            </div>
            <div xml:id="T04_AD_F.67_Naameh_Maslaxbefore4_a20">
               <u xml:lang="ar-acm-x-shawi-vicav"
                  who="corpus:LEB_KAR_2022_KZ_M.27_Speaker12"
                  xml:id="T04_AD_F.67_Naameh_Maslaxbefore4_a20_u1"
                  end="#T11"
                  start="#T10">
                  <w join="right"
                     xml:id="T04_AD_F.67_Naameh_Maslaxbefore4_xTok_000027"
                     xml:lang="ar-acm-x-shawi-vicav">ṣaḥīḥ</w>
                  <pc xml:id="xTok_000028">.</pc>
               </u>
               <spanGrp type="Translation">
                  <span xml:lang="en"
                        target="#T04_AD_F.67_Naameh_Maslaxbefore4_a20"
                        xml:id="a46">Right.</span>
               </spanGrp>
            </div>
            <div xml:id="T04_AD_F.67_Naameh_Maslaxbefore4_a52">
               <u xml:lang="ar-acm-x-shawi-vicav"
                  who="corpus:LEB_KAR_2022_KZ_M.27_Speaker12"
                  xml:id="T04_AD_F.67_Naameh_Maslaxbefore4_a52_u1"
                  end="#T13"
                  start="#T12">
                  <w join="right"
                     xml:id="T04_AD_F.67_Naameh_Maslaxbefore4_xTok_000029"
                     xml:lang="ar-acm-x-shawi-vicav"
                     rendition="rend:dashAfter">y</w>
                  <w xml:id="T04_AD_F.67_Naameh_Maslaxbefore4_xTok_000031"
                     xml:lang="ar-acm-x-shawi-vicav">amīn</w>
                  <w xml:id="T04_AD_F.67_Naameh_Maslaxbefore4_xTok_000032"
                     xml:lang="ar-acm-x-shawi-vicav">ya</w>
                  <w join="right"
                     xml:id="T04_AD_F.67_Naameh_Maslaxbefore4_xTok_000033"
                     xml:lang="ar-acm-x-shawi-vicav">rabb</w>
                  <pc xml:id="xTok_000034">.</pc>
               </u>
               <spanGrp type="Translation">
                  <span xml:lang="en"
                        target="#T04_AD_F.67_Naameh_Maslaxbefore4_a52"
                        xml:id="a53">Amen, oh lord.</span>
               </spanGrp>
            </div>
            <div xml:id="T04_AD_F.67_Naameh_Maslaxbefore4_a21">
               <u xml:lang="ar-acm-x-shawi-vicav"
                  who="corpus:LEB_NAA_2023_AD_F.67_Speaker1"
                  xml:id="T04_AD_F.67_Naameh_Maslaxbefore4_a21_u1"
                  end="#T40"
                  start="#T39">
                  <gap reason="unconsented"/>
               </u>
               <spanGrp type="Translation">
                  <span xml:lang="en"
                        target="#T04_AD_F.67_Naameh_Maslaxbefore4_a21"
                        xml:id="a47">My dear.</span>
               </spanGrp>
            </div>
         </div>
      </body>
   </text>
